<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.7.7">
<l>paṭarpaṅka yamalarvāy nekiḻap paṉipaṭu ciṟutuḷipō</l>
<l>liṭaṅkoṇ ṭacevvā yūṟiyūṟi yiṟṟiṟṟu vīḻaniṉṟu</l>
<l>kaṭuñcēkka ḻuttiṉma ṇikkuraṟpō luṭaimaṇi kaṇakaṇeṉa</l>
<l>taṭantāḷi ṇaikoṇṭucārṅ kapāṇi taḷarnaṭai naṭavāṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While [the nectar] continuously oozes, dribbles, and drips</l>
<l>from [his] vast red mouth like the small drops</l>
<l>that appear as dew when the expanding lotus blossom fully blooms,</l>
<l>while the bells on [his] waist jingle</l>
<l>like the bells on the neck of the ferocious bull,</l>
<l>will he who bears the Sarṅga bow</l>
<l>come with a tottering walk with [his] pair of broad feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
